snippet.title: Star Stuff - Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
A cosmic mix of tactic automation and real-time action for players of all kinds! Take on the role of an engineer in a galactic star factory: Program helpful bots, work with them to solve puzzles, keep the factory running, and save the universe along the way.

Wishlist Star Stuff now! 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1955110/Star_Stuff/

Follow us on Twitter! ✨
